    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's just standard procedure for the new ISO compliance. The regulators are worried about complex reasoning causing unexpected maneuvers in edge cases, so they want us on a more predictable, script-based system. It's not up for debate, we just need to get the transition done.",
